Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:05.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这不可能\N{\fnArial\fs48}This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，你回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿，史蒂仔\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Steve-O.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们对之前的事非常抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're so sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}别管这些了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们必须追上她！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We have to catch up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:14.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:14.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谁？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蓝钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blue Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蓝钻石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blue Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}噢，哦，不，在地球？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, oh, on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:21.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我的天！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Holy smokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她们总算要现身了\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're all coming out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶，变成把椅子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, turn into a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我得坐下来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I need to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她带走了爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She took Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她像外星人一样绑架了他，而这都是我的错！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She alien abducted him, and it's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她抓走了格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs48}She took Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们的格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}难道还有别的格雷格？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What other Greg is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们该怎么将他带回来？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How are we gonna get him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:39.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她甚至要他有什么用？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What does she even want him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}吃掉他？将他放进动物园？\N{\fnArial\fs48}To eat him? To put him in a zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:43.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还真可能是这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}That might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她会吃了他？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's gonna eat him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么？不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但确实有个-不，不，\N{\fnArial\fs48}But there was a -- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:52.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但不可能仍然还在\N{\fnArial\fs48}It couldn't possibly still exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}至少从我们-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not since we --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:54.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:57.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}粉钻石隐秘的人类动物园\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pink Diamond's insidious human zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:58.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当她还在地球时，\N{\fnArial\fs48}During her reign on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:02.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}粉钻石将人类从他们的家人旁掠走\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pink Diamond stole humans from their families
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:04.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}作为她征程的一个奖杯\N{\fnArial\fs48}as trophies of her conquests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:06.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你一定是在开玩笑吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:07.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，不\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:08.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是真的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:10.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当我还在服务于...母世界\N{\fnArial\fs48}When I still served... Homeworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我亲眼看到的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I saw it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一个深空中的私人野生动物园\N{\fnArial\fs48}A private menagerie deep in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}人类被困在其中\N{\fnArial\fs48}Humans in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们一直没能救他们出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We were never able to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}战争开始后我们一直没有能力接近他们\N{\fnArial\fs48}We had no way to get to them after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但这是五千年前了\N{\fnArial\fs48}But that was over 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:26.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你真的确定格雷格在那里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You really think Greg's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，蓝钻石想让他活着？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, Blue Diamond wanted him alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对，是的！她很喜欢他！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, yes! She liked him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我想不出还有什么地方她会安置他\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't think of anywhere else she'd put him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:34.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果她想留着他，\N{\fnArial\fs48}if she wanted to keep him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果动物园还在的话，\N{\fnArial\fs48}That is if the zoo's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}只能去那里试试了\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我们该怎么到那里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But how are we going to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:42.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}用the Roaming Eye\N{\fnArial\fs48}With the Roaming Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}红宝石的太空船？\N{\fnArial\fs48}The Ruby ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:46.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们要前往太空了，\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're going into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且我们一定要带回格雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}and we're not coming back without Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们的中子星定位器仍然在定位\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your pulsar trackers are tracking pulsars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}大气防护层看起来还能工作\N{\fnArial\fs48}The atmosphere shield seems functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但你们在太空中用不到那个，显然\N{\fnArial\fs48}but you're not going to need that in space, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}确保这对史蒂文是安全的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Make sure it's safe for Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他应该没问题，\N{\fnArial\fs48}He should be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我认为我得更改\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I think I should go in and change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}红宝石们设定的系统偏好\N{\fnArial\fs48}the system preferences the Rubies set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你感觉绿光相比红光怎么样\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do you feel about green lights instead of red?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没时间搞这些了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果能用的话，咱们赶紧干！\N{\fnArial\fs48}If it works, - let's just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起，康妮，但我们等不及了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, Connie, but we just can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸身陷困境\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad's in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且我们得前往太空将他带回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}and we need to go into space to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们现在就走\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're going right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一定要在我们离开后保护好沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just protect Beach City for me while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:26.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么，如果我输入坐标，\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, if I input the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:27.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}它就会直接带我们过去？\N{\fnArial\fs48}it will take us right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}实际上更复杂一些\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a little more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这不是你们那种第一代的“轻型风筝”\N{\fnArial\fs48}These aren't your era one light kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们很可能会“扭曲现实”\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're gonna be pretty much bending reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果要用引力引擎的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}if you turn on the gravity engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}考虑到这个，我真的该\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come to think of it, I should really change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一起更改红宝石对那个设置的偏好\N{\fnArial\fs48}the ruby preferences on that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所以呢？那个设的是红色！\N{\fnArial\fs48}So what? So it's red!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}快啊，快点！我们得走了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, come on! We got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}先不管红宝石，它能飞起来吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rubies aside, will it fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}简单来说，可以\N{\fnArial\fs48}Short answer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么，出发！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}青金石，橄榄石，留在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis, Peridot, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们得保护沙滩市\N{\fnArial\fs48}You'll have to protect Beach City
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}以防我们离开时有事发生\N{\fnArial\fs48}if something happens while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们可以相信我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can count on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不要担心，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:09.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们已经在路上了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我真希望他能看到这样的风景\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hope he got to see some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这里的风光足够填满\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's enough out here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一整个有关宇宙的专辑了\N{\fnArial\fs48}for a whole album about the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}太空涡流\N{\fnArial\fs48}Space turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}飞的不错嘛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sweet moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧，我们还要飞多远-\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right, how much further till we get to --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:38.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:44.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起，红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, Rubies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们真的该对她们做点什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}We should really do something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们能在回来的路上接她们\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can pick them up on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸是首要任务\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还有多久我们能到那里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How much longer till we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，按现在的速度\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, at our current speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:58.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们到达人类动物园应该在...\N{\fnArial\fs48}we should be reaching the human zoo in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}大约七十人类年之后\N{\fnArial\fs48}approximately 70 human years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}刚好赶上格雷格的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just in time for Greg's 110th anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:03.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}110大寿\N{\fnArial\fs48}of being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}珍珠，我爸的身体状况\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, my dad's not healthy enough
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}坚持不了那么久\N{\fnArial\fs48}to live that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:12.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃...你觉得我们能把时间砍到69年吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...do you think he'll be able to make it to 109?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们走之前\N{\fnArial\fs48}Before we left,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:15.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}橄榄石提到了引力引擎\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot did mention a gravity engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，对啊，她说那会“扭曲现实”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, yeah. She said it bends reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}噢，我确定她是在夸大其词\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I'm sure she was exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这很可能只是改变速度的定义\N{\fnArial\fs48}It probably just alters the definition of speed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}通过操纵时空来达成，\N{\fnArial\fs48}by manipulating space time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但这对有机物质会有什么影响？\N{\fnArial\fs48}but what effect will that have on organic matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这有可能会扁平化史蒂文的身体\N{\fnArial\fs48}It might flatten Steven's body
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}将其变成由皮肤和骨骼组成的烙饼\N{\fnArial\fs48}into a pancake of skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}骨头很恶心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bones are gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你卧室里可有骨头\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have bones in your bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那不一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那是我的骨头\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those are my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果变成烙饼能拯救我爸爸，\N{\fnArial\fs48}If being a pancake means saving my dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么，端上酱汁吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}then bring on the syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文？你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我感觉我刚刚晕了过去\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think I just blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:02.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，你们还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你说呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，不，有地方不对\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh,{\i1} no,{\i} we're{\i1} not{\i} okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，为什么你们看起来怪怪的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, why do you guys look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:13.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}引力传送似乎对我们的身体有影响\N{\fnArial\fs48}The gravity warp seems to be affecting our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一定要告诉我这会有持久的效果\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please tell me this lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们的身体是由光组成的，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our bodies are made of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而通常光会制造出质量\N{\fnArial\fs48}and usually they form a mass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这取决于周围的气压\N{\fnArial\fs48}dependent on the air pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}与引力状况\N{\fnArial\fs48}and the level of gravity in the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我们身处的情况\N{\fnArial\fs48}But we're in a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不适用于一般的物理规则\N{\fnArial\fs48}where the normal laws of physics don't apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谁在乎呢？反正很有趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who cares? It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这怎么有趣了？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}In what way is this funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么，你们不是故意这么做的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, you guys aren't doing this on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们不能通过变形变回去吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can't you shapeshift back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哈，快看，美洲狮崽\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh, check it out. Puma cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}飞船似乎通过散发某种能量\N{\fnArial\fs48}The ship seems to be putting out some kind of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我们保持现在的尺寸\N{\fnArial\fs48}keeping us in this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，我知道该怎么做了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I know the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}橄榄石说这艘船是按红宝石校准的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot said the ship was calibrated for Rubies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这肯定让你们都变成了红宝石的大小\N{\fnArial\fs48}It must be making you all Ruby sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊！为什么她从不告诉我们任何事？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh! Why doesn't she ever tell us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这就是为什么我们不要听她的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is why we don't listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:05.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许我能更改设置\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe I can change the settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不是\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:20.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这好像行不通\N{\fnArial\fs48}This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}试试手动调节\N{\fnArial\fs48}Try adjusting it manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔，呃，也许是这个？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa. Um, maybe this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧，所以它是干这个的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, so that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许是这个？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊！为什么要搞得这么复杂？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! Why is this so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这开始变得有点怪了，即使对我也是\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is getting a little weird, even for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我好像发现关闭按钮了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think I found the off switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}伙计们！我-我做什么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Guys! W-What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶？石榴？珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst? Garnet? Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}发生什么了？你们碎了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What happened? Are you cracked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:27.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶通常已经恢复了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst is usually back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦，不！那是动物园\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no. That's the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，我们要直接跟动物园撞上了，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, we're gonna smash right into it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:41.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果还不减速的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}if we don't slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}上啊，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你能做到的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这没什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}宝石人们没事的\N{\fnArial\fs48}The gems are gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她们不会出事的\N{\fnArial\fs48}They got to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸也不会出事的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad's gonna be fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}虽然现在看起来不是这样，\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't seem like it right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但待会，我们会在一起欢笑的\N{\fnArial\fs48}but later, we're gonna laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}只要我能让太空船停下\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I could just stop the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}它不会停下的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It isn't going to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没法解决这个问题\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's no fixing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这都是我的错\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我太着急了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I rushed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:34.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我逼着大家做出愚蠢又错误的决定\N{\fnArial\fs48}I pushed us into making stupid mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}本不用这样的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It didn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我本应听石榴的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}I didn't have to not listen to Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不应去韩国\N{\fnArial\fs48}I didn't have to go to Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不应让你被蓝钻石永远带走\N{\fnArial\fs48}I didn't have to get you taken away forever by Blue Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我不是出于自私\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I wasn't trying to be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:57.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我这次只是想搞清都发生了什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just wanted to know what was going on for myself for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但现在我失去了所有人\N{\fnArial\fs48}But now I lost everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我想我的爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我只想见到我爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just want my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}之前去哪了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我之前非常担心！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我想你试图恢复我们身体的举动\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think in your attempt to fix our bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许意外的\N{\fnArial\fs48}you may have accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}关闭了所有的校准\N{\fnArial\fs48}shut off the calibration altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:46.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们由光组成的外形无法跟上\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our light-composed forms couldn't keep up with a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}超过光速移动的飞船\N{\fnArial\fs48}moving faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:52.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所以你们刚才只是一直落在飞船后方？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So you were just lagging behind the ship this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是啊，不要太担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. Don't worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶很喜欢这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我从没想到我能伸展到那么远\N{\fnArial\fs48}I never thought I could stretch so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我感觉我貌似直接贯穿了某个星球！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think I kind of phased through a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃，史小子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, yo, Ste-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你听到石榴说的话了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You heard Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们完全没事，哥们\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're totally fine, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我太心急了，我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I was pushing so hard,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我只是非常想见到我爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just wanted to get Dad back so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我-我几乎搞砸了整个任务\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I almost wrecked the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:20.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这都是我的错\N{\fnArial\fs48}This whole thing is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文，不是你绑架的格雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you didn't kidnap Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是蓝钻石做的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blue Diamond did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:29.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔，你们看到了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa. Do you guys see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你所做的带我们到了动物园\N{\fnArial\fs48}What you did got us to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且只是提前了70人类年而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}And only 70 human years ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很快会见到你的，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll see you really soon, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我希望\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,
